      <title>朝鲜抨击卢比奥“粗鲁”言论，誓言予以强硬回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/north-korea-slams-rubio-s-coarse-remarks-vows-tough-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜强烈谴责美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥最近将平壤描述为“流氓”国家，并誓言“绝不容忍”华盛顿的任何挑衅行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/north-korea-slams-rubio-s-coarse-remarks-vows-tough-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:48:33 GMT</pubDate>
